  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Every child has the right to education. ECD4ALL is calling for action to make this a reality. We are focusing our work on the most vulnerable children living in South Africa&apos;s informal settlements. 75% of 8 million children between 0 - 6 years old are still not equal in accessing quality Early Childhood Development services. In the informal settlement of Monwabisi Park, 227 children have access to a formal ECD program. This project prepares teachers to serve the 473 children still excluded.</narrative>
  </description>
